{
  "text": "Remark 2. All our proofs (see [CITATION_1] ) still go through when the process X n is replaced by inf(sup(X n , \u2212A), A) in equation (1) for some large A. Such a modification is an easy trick to render Assumptions (H1) easier to fulfill.",
